---

That's everything needed at the root. Your final structure should be:
```
SentinelIDS/
├── docker-compose.yml   ← new
├── README.md            ← new
├── .gitignore           ← new
├── backend/             ← existing
└── frontend/            ← your existing or the sentinelui zip